== Expression Language

DFLib expression language is a special syntax that the library can parse to an `Exp` object. Parsing a single expression
is done with the `Exp.parseExp(String)` method:

[source,java,indent=0]
----
include::../../../test/java/org/dflib/docs/ExpLangTest.java[tags=parseExp]
